data.title: University of Pennsylvania Athletics
data.meta_description: Dan HowardMD  - 2005-06: Placed 55th at the Heptagonal Championships (10/28) ... Finished 74th at Penn State (10/15) ... Placed 24th at the Fordham Invitational
data.text:
2005-06: Placed 55th at the Heptagonal Championships (10/28) ... Finished 74th at Penn State (10/15) ... Placed 24th at the Fordham Invitational (9/10).

2004-05: Took sixth in the 5,000m at the Quaker Invitational ... Named to the Dean's List.

High School: Four time letterwinner in cross country and track and earned one letter in tennis ... 2004 indoor track District, Region, and State 1600m champion ... 2004 outdoor track District and Region 1600m champion ... 2003 First team All-State in cross country ... 2002,2003, 2004 Academic All District and Region in both indoor and outdoor track ... 2002, 2003, 2004 All State and All America in indoor track ... 2002, 2003, 2004 outdoor track All State ... Member of both National Honor Society and National Latin Honor Society .
